      "rationale": "The model employs linear elastic Ti-6Al-4V material with large-displacement formulation and nonlinear frictional contact at the screw-rod interface. Sensitivity analyses confirm that plasticity effects are negligible below yield force, and geometric nonlinearity is captured. Model form is appropriate for the COU, meeting gradation 3."
