      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and Poisson's ratio were measured from tensile coupons of the same material lot as the test constructs. Geometry was captured via CMM with traceable calibration. Input uncertainty was propagated through a Monte Carlo analysis confirming that input variability contributes less than 3% to QoI uncertainty, meeting gradation 3."
