      "rationale": "Testing was conducted per ASTM F1717 at a single quasi-static load rate and single fixation configuration. While the standard protocol was followed rigorously across two independent laboratories, only one test condition was evaluated. This limits the achieved level to gradation 2, one below the required gradation 3. This gap is noted and accepted given the standardized nature of the ASTM protocol."
