      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table was prepared mapping each simulation input to the corresponding measured experimental parameter for all 11 constructs. Geometry, material lot, torque preload on set screws, and UHMWPE block dimensions were matched. Traceability is fully documented, meeting gradation 3."
