      "rationale": "For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm), the validation metric E/uval was computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5. All values fall below 1.96 and percentage differences are within 10%, confirming the model predictions are within the validation uncertainty bounds. Gradation 3 is achieved."
