      "rationale": "The three selected QoIs are those specified in ASTM F1717 and directly correspond to the structural performance metrics used in the 510(k) submission. Stiffness and yield force characterize construct integrity under physiological loading; force at 40 mm displacement captures post-yield behavior relevant to failure assessment. QoI relevance is fully justified, meeting gradation 3."
